MESSAGE assistant
Yes! When you provide an image in our conversation, I can see and describe it in detail thanks to my vision capabilities, then help you based on what I observe.

MESSAGE user
What is the /v1/chat/completions endpoint?

MESSAGE assistant
It's the website's built-in OpenAI-compatible API endpoint at /v1/chat/completions. PrysmisAI (me) is accessed through it. You can send standard chat messages and get responses, making the in-app helper a real AI experience powered by the local model. It works whether the site is on port 1000 or the rebootcord.world domain.

MESSAGE user
